  "instructions": [
    "In a large pot, bring the water to a boil and cook the rice vermicelli according to package instructions.",
    "In a separate pan, heat the vegetable oil over medium heat and saute the onion until translucent.",
    "Add the garlic to the pan and cook for an additional minute.",
    "In a large bowl, combine the cooked rice vermicelli, sauteed onion and garlic, and long-fermentation-dough.",
    "Season with black pepper and salt to taste.",
    "Toss everything together until well combined.",
    "Serve hot and enjoy.",
    "Garnish with additional black pepper if desired."
